AMANITH FRAMEWORK README
************************
Crossplatform, Opensource, Ansi C++, Framework aimed to handle 2d and 3d Vector Graphic.

 =------------------------=
 | Version: 1.0b          |
 | Released: 30 June 2005 |
 | Licence: QPL           |
 | Url: www.amanith.org   |
 =------------------------=

Contents of the package
=======================

