Third parts libraries
=====================

FreeType2 v2.1.10 (www.freetype.org)

LibJpeg v6b (ftp.uu.net/graphics/jpeg/)

LibPng v1.2.7 (www.libpng.org/pub/png/)

ZLib v1.2.2 (http://www.gzip.org/zlib/)

Glew v1.3.3 (glew.sourceforge.net)
